{
  "stem": "3658.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He forgot to wake me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were looking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they looked for you and found you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With dogs, oh!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the SS, they found me there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So of course, I got-- I got a terrible hiding from them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we came into the camp-- see, they-- they report to the camp commandants, so this is-- this is, either you get killed, shot, or whatever, or big punishment.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my punishment was I stood in front of the electrified wires for a  whole day not moving.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the-- the bashing that I got before-- it's too horrible.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What did they do to you?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they-- they-- they-- they beat me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They hit me, and I was bleeding and everything, because they-- they, you know, with a-- with a stick, that they had to-- to go-- I mean--",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Looking for you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's unheard of to go looking for you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that was the experience there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they put-- put us, the younger ones-- because they-- they-- they-- there were other younger people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As I said, one of them is alive here, which I'll come to it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They put us in what they called [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Potatoes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Peeling potatoes-- but not peeling, but cutting potatoes in a-- in a-- in a sort of-- for the camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were mostly the younger ones-- as I said, my age group-- and we must have been about-- about 20 of us there around big-- big sort of-- we were sitting around chairs, I remember, and there was water that you put it in.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, you take-- took it to a-- a big other-- like a samovar.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not a samovar.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like a-- like a bath, but huge, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
